# Apple ID / iCloud 鉴权域名 —— 强制 DIRECT
# 放在所有 ruleset 之前，绝对优先级直连
# 解决 Apple ID 登录失败 / iCloud 验证失败 / 设备激活鉴权走代理问题

# --- 账号鉴权核心（登录失败首要相关）---
DOMAIN,gsa.apple.com
DOMAIN,gs.apple.com
DOMAIN,gsas.apple.com
DOMAIN,setup.icloud.com
DOMAIN,gateway.icloud.com
DOMAIN,appleid.apple.com
DOMAIN,idmsa.apple.com
DOMAIN,appleid.cdn-apple.com
DOMAIN,p01-quota.icloud.com
DOMAIN,p01-keyvalueservice.icloud.com

# --- 推送 / 设备激活 ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,push.apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,push-apple.com.akadns.net
DOMAIN,albert.apple.com
DOMAIN,captive.apple.com

# --- iCloud 全域 ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,icloud.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,icloud-content.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,me.com

# --- Apple 主域 / CDN ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cdn-apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mzstatic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,aaplimg.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,apple-cloudkit.com

# --- App Store / 验证 ---
DOMAIN,xp.apple.com
DOMAIN,init.itunes.apple.com
DOMAIN,doh.dns.apple.com
